<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <title>AI Mole Scanner | Advanced Skin Health Monitoring by Eoria Apps</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Discover AI Mole Scanner. Use professional-grade AI technology for early skin spot analysis and dermatology tracking. Powered by Eoria Apps.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="AI mole scanner, skin cancer detection app, dermatology AI, melanoma tracking, Eoria Apps health">
    
    <meta property="og:title" content="AI Mole Scanner - Smart Skin Analysis">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Professional AI-driven skin health monitoring at your fingertips.">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #e0e5ec;
            --text-color: #44475a;
            --accent-color: #007AFF;
            --shadow-light: -9px -9px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
            --shadow-dark: 9px 9px 16px rgba(163, 177, 198, 0.6);
            --shadow-inset: inset 6px 6px 12px rgba(163, 177, 198, 0.5), 
                            inset -6px -6px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-color); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: var(--text-color); overflow-x: hidden; }

        /* Navigation */
        nav { padding: 25px; display: flex; justify-content: center; position: sticky; top: 0; background: var(--bg-color); z-index: 100; }
        .nav-inner { width: 100%; max-width: 1200px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .back-link { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-color); font-weight: 600; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-light), var(--shadow-dark); }

        /* 1. Header with Graphics (Hero) */
        .hero { padding: 80px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .hero-graphic {
            width: 280px; height: 280px; margin: 0 auto 40px;
            background: var(--bg-color); border-radius: 60px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-light), var(--shadow-dark);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .pulse-circle {
            width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--bg-color); box-shadow: var(--shadow-inset);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 3rem;
        }
        .scanner-line {
            position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 4px; background: var(--accent-color);
            top: 50%; opacity: 0.5; box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-color);
            animation: scan 3s infinite ease-in-out;
        }
        @keyframes scan { 0%, 100% { top: 20%; } 50% { top: 80%; } }

        h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -2px; }

        /* 2. Description Section */
        .section-desc { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 100px; text-align: center; padding: 0 20px; }
        .section-desc p { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0.8; }

        /* 3. Technology Description */
        .tech-box { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 100px; padding: 20px; }
        .tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; }
        .card { padding: 40px; border-radius: 35px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-light), var(--shadow-dark); background: var(--bg-color); }
        .card h3 { margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-color); }

        /* 4. Tech Links (List) */
        .tech-links { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50px; margin: 0 20px 100px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-inset); }
        .tech-links h2 { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .tag-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; }
        .tag { padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 50px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-light), var(--shadow-dark); text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-color); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .tag:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-inset); color: var(--accent-color); }

        /* 5. Visual Footer Graphic */
        .footer-graphic { padding: 100px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .app-preview-container { 
            max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px; border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-light), var(--shadow-dark);
        }
        .cta-btn { 
            display: inline-block; margin-top: 40px; padding: 25px 60px; 
            background: var(--bg-color); border-radius: 50px; 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-light), var(--shadow-dark);
            text-decoration: none; color: var(--accent-color); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.3rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .cta-btn:active { box-shadow: var(--shadow-inset); transform: scale(0.98); }

        footer { padding: 50px; text-align: center; opacity: 0.4; font-size: 0.9rem; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .hero-graphic { width: 200px; height: 200px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="nav-inner">
            <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← Eoria Apps</a>
            <div class="logo">AI<span>Mole</span></div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <header class="hero">
            <div class="hero-graphic">
                <div class="pulse-circle">🔍</div>
                <div class="scanner-line"></div>
            </div>
            <h1>AI Mole Scanner</h1>
        </header>

        <section class="section-desc">
            <p>
                <strong>AI Mole Scanner</strong> is a cutting-edge dermatological tool designed for early monitoring of skin changes. 
                Using deep learning models, the app allows users to capture high-resolution images of moles and track their 
                evolution over time, providing a data-driven approach to skin health and melanoma prevention.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="tech-box">
            <div class="tech-grid">
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Computer Vision</h3>
                    <p>Our custom neural networks are trained on 100,000+ clinical images to detect asymmetrical patterns and border irregularities with high precision.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Privacy First</h3>
                    <p>All image processing is encrypted. We use on-device processing where possible to ensure your sensitive health data never leaves your control.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>History Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Compare photos side-by-side using our proprietary alignment technology to notice even the slightest changes in size or color.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="tech-links">
            <h2>Core Technology Stack</h2>
            <div class="tag-container">
                <a href="#" class="tag">TensorFlow ML</a>
                <a href="#" class="tag">CoreML 3.0</a>
                <a href="#" class="tag">Computer Vision API</a>
                <a href="#" class="tag">Python Integration</a>
                <a href="#" class="tag">Encrypted Cloud Storage</a>
                <a href="#" class="tag">Dermatoscopic Analysis</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="footer-graphic">
            <div class="app-preview-container">
                <h2>Ready to track your health?</h2>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;">Join thousands of users prioritizing their skin safety today.</p>
                <a href="https://apple.com/app-store" class="cta-btn">Go to App Store</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 Eoria Apps | AI Mole Scanner Project. For informational purposes only.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
